edge: The article 'Main article: Andhadhun (soundtrack)' provides further details about the music in the movie 'Andhadhun'.
The title track of the soundtrack of 'Andhadhun' was composed by Raftaar and Girish Nakod.
The remainder of the 'Andhadhun' soundtrack was composed by Amit Trivedi.
The lyrics for the 'Andhadhun' soundtrack were written by Jaideep Sahni.
The lyrics for the title track of the 'Andhadhun' soundtrack were written by Raftaar and Girish Nakod.
The lyrics for the title track of the 'Andhadhun' soundtrack were written by Raftaar and Girish Nakod.
The vocals for the remainder of the 'Andhadhun' soundtrack were provided by Amit Trivedi.
The vocals for the title track of the 'Andhadhun' soundtrack were provided by Raftaar.
The vocals for some songs in the 'Andhadhun' soundtrack were provided by Ayushmann Khurrana.
The vocals for some songs in the 'Andhadhun' soundtrack were provided by Arijit Singh.
The vocals for some songs in the 'Andhadhun' soundtrack were provided by Abhijeet Srivastava.
The vocals for some songs in the 'Andhadhun' soundtrack were provided by Aakansha Sharma.
The vocals for some songs in the 'Andhadhun' soundtrack were provided by Shadab Faridi.
The vocals for some songs in the 'Andhadhun' soundtrack were provided by Altamash Faridi.
The background score of the movie 'Andhadhun' was composed by Daniel B. George.
